text: Julie Beaulieu (born 28 April 1983) is a Canadian gymnast. She competed in six events at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Canada Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Montreal Category:Pan American Games medalists in gymnastics Category:Pan American Games gold medalists for Canada Category:Pan American Games silver medalists for Canada Category:Gymnasts at the 1999 Pan American Games
